<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Food-security/Related-developments/Uganda-A-Trying-Year-for-Agriculture" title="Uganda: A Trying Year for Agriculture" alt="link">Uganda: A Trying Year for Agriculture</a></h2>

	
					<p>Last year was not a pleasant one for the agriculture sector. The food crisis reached unbearable levels in many parts of the country, largely due to poor weather and a failed harvest in 2007. Farm input prices sky-rocketed, affecting farmers and animal food producers. (Source: Joshua Kato, New Vision, 31 December 2008).</p>
